lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1000</span>多个收费标准。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-indent: 28.1pt; line-height: 16pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312\\\\\">本县范围内面向企业的行政事业性收费项目，一律以本《汇编》为准，凡未列入《汇编》及《汇编》所列的文件依据中未规定的行政事业性收费项目一律不得向企业收费，企业有权拒付。《汇编》截止日期为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2011</span>年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">11</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>日，以后设立的行政事业性收费项目或调整的收费标准按照国家和省规范性收费文件的规定执行。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-indent: 28.1pt; line-height: 16pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312\\\\\">价格举报电话：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12358</span></span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; line-height: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp; </font></span></span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312\\\\\">嘉鱼县物价局　<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\